eo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/95b865c235a3107a11158bc29f3831e7.poster.avif?t=1735748515\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/95b865c235a3107a11158bc29f3831e7.webm?t=1735748515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/95b865c235a3107a11158bc29f3831e7.mp4?t=1735748515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HONE YOUR AIM AND UNLEASH YOUR GAME</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/75383fcbf54f4ce8ad1c66973cf2070e.poster.avif?t=1735748515\" width=640 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/75383fcbf54f4ce8ad1c66973cf2070e.webm?t=1735748515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/75383fcbf54f4ce8ad1c66973cf2070e.mp4?t=1735748515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Matchmaking<strong> are ranked based on the overall skill of all team members. You can play a matchmaking game solo, and you'll be automatically placed in a team with an available slot, or you can set up your own team and invite your friends.<br><br><strong>Multiplayer</strong> mode will allow you to create your own custom match. The 2 modes available there:<br>1)\t<strong>Classic mode</strong> - 2 teams playing against each other. The team who scores more goals before the period is over, wins.<br>2)\t<strong>Mordor mode</strong> - 4 teams playing against each other. Each team has a number of lives. If one team concedes a goal, they lose one life. If they lose all the lives, they drop out of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR STYLE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/bc8fcf877a6090af5444c12a24f3514f.poster.avif?t=1735748515\" width=360 height=203 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174420/extras/bc8fcf877a6090af5444c12a24f3514f.webm?t=1735748515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Singleplayer</strong> mode is divided into three categories. In the first category, you will practice accuracy and ball control. In the second category, you will play soccer-golf. The third category will require you to heavily rely on your ball-handling skills to overcome a variety of challenging obstacles. After mastering each section, bonus levels await to challenge and reward you.<br><br><strong>Coop or Solo</strong> call on a friend to help you win the trophy and defeat the long-armed goalkeeper.</strong></strong>",
